# Temporary files
tmp/
.tmp/

# goreleaser
dist/
# internal/web/dist/ is a generated build artifact produced by
# `task web:embed` (runs `pnpm build` and copies web/build/ into it).
# It is ignored entirely. The default `go build` uses
# internal/web/placeholder/ via `//go:build !realweb`, so a fresh checkout
# compiles without requiring the SvelteKit pipeline to have run yet.
# `task build` / `task docker:build` pass `-tags realweb` to embed the
# real bundle from dist/ after web:embed has populated it.

